summary: Do you guys have any comics about groot or goose captain marvel's cat?
question: Do you guys have any comics about groot or goose captain marvel's cat?
answer: Groot has been appearing in Guardians of the Galaxy comic for several years, including the latest series. We have several versions of that book in stock. He also had a solo miniseries in 2015 called Groot, a later miniseries called I am Groot, and even a series with Rocket in 2016 called Rocket Racoon and Groot. Goose the…“cat” (named “Chewy” in the comics, but still the same character) has been appearing in various Captain Marvel comics since the character was first identified as an alien in 2014. Let us know what you would like! Your best bet for accurate accounts of what we have in stock at a given moment is to call the stores directly. We can be reached in Mechanicsburg at 717-591-2727, or York at 717-767-4871.

title: Marvel and Webs
body:
An update on the kittens I found yesterday! [the previous post is here x]

I got very little sleep last night, but the kittens are both doing well today, and I just returned from taking them to a no-kill shelter.

The people at the shelter are going to look after them, and even have a mama cat they’re hoping will take in the little guy.

Since the bigger girl kitty is a damn hero, and the little guy has a lot of fight in him, I told the shelter their names are Marvel and Webs, after Captain Marvel and Spider-Man :)
